# user-data: runbook .md files (SORACK_RUNBOOKS_DIR default in dev pod).
# Content is operator-owned, not part of the codebase. Leading slash so the
# pattern only matches the repo-root `runbooks/`, not the `api/src/runbooks/`
# code module.
/runbooks/
# Same idea for alt dirs used during e2e git testing (operator points
# SORACK_RUNBOOKS_DIR at one of these temporarily).
/runbooks-*/
